===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A pin inserted through holes at the end of an axle or shaft, so as to secure a wheel or shaft-mounted device.
#* '''1376–7''',  ''Compotus Roll Hyde Manor'' (In the manuscript deeds of Westminster Abbey)
